{"title":"Ertapenem-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Urología/Ertapenem-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Ertapenem","guid":"FSl5QSvuWS6haH3I2pjAKg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Tipo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Carbapenem ⬇️ Aerobios y anaerobios Gram (-)","guid":"bHCzYu5r1wKVhbtjsxMM9A","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• No efectivo contra P. aeruginosa","guid":"TOjFLyXfcuW42Q6QwQxf3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"0","text":"Uso Clínico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• FDA aprobado: NAC, ITU complicadas, inf. pélvicas, piel/estructuras cutáneas, profilaxis cx colorrectal.","guid":"XbRu0SAedbsFExpqiTHTQQ","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Alternativa para genotipos resistentes.","guid":"wAYMFU7jkbdDFeZHOHNgTw","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Vía de Administración:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• IV/IM (IM diluido con lidocaína)","guid":"Gy9J1PYrK32M8vowCacsmw","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"Dosis:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• Adultos: 1 g IV/IM q24h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"• Pediátricos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"•  28 días: 30 mg/kg/día (dividido q12h), máx. 1 g/día.","guid":"xEjSrRrM0BLJ0asj9vLfMA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"0","text":"Ajuste Renal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• T1/2 (Función renal normal): 4 hrs.","guid":"nzY1jJio64Vk5NsDrCPxtg","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• T1/2 (ESRD): >4 hrs.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"• CrCl >30 mL/min/1. 73 m²: Sin ajuste.","guid":"t_xPVNNnl54kRUI7LXX6iQ","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"13","text":"• CrCl ≤30 mL/min/1.73 m²: 500 mg q24h.","guid":"MXIZhVROvTKxHreVjfku7Q","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"13","text":"• Hemodiálisis: 500 mg q24h +150 mg AD si <6 hrs antes de HD.","guid":"DNbjG2Z6zuzC_KGPl-g30Q","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"13","text":"• CAPD: 500 mg q24h.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"13","text":"• CRRT: 0.5-1 g q24h.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"13","text":"• SLED: 1 g q24h.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Ajuste Hepático:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• No requiere.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"0","text":"Ajuste en Obesidad:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• ↑ Dosis en obesidad extrema o MIC elevada\\N(p.ej., 1.5 g q24h en paciente 250 kg con NAC).","guid":"IUXG_l2hglCEa2-x7bw29A","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"Efectos\\NAdversos:","guid":"iOsf6oVOpcw7HxpkCvXWVw","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• GI: Náuseas/vómitos (3%), diarrea (6%).","guid":"W6Fci_ysUdtPBQwD4GFFhQ","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Hepático: ↑ LFTs (6%).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• Neurológico: Cefalea (2%), neurotoxicidad (p.ej., convulsiones), alucinaciones visuales.","guid":"wAATtrO5-rdKqU5qpi63sA","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"• Hipersensibilidad: Fiebre, rash, anafilaxia, DRESS.","guid":"r1qjdIxkilHsQKYVB_uOIA","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"• Hematológico: Coombs (+) (1%), neutropenia, eosinofilia.","guid":"rqqzTUonvaoB0hei0bZneg","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"26","text":"• Músculo: Debilidad muscular.","guid":"yonT7jOAVY7V_XCqPZ2b_Q","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"26","text":"• Local: Flebitis (4%), rxn. hipersensibilidad a lidocaína.","guid":"9LLuGR-ltA3kxLpPjez5Tw","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"26","text":"• Revisión de casos: neurotoxicidad (125 casos) (1).","guid":"6eWWs10pFUYGdCqcfDC8vQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"Embarazo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Categoría de Riesgo: Insuficiente evidencia en humanos, no tóxico en animales.","guid":"ocgjH7HNwi_pMzgJGgk8Vw","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"0","text":"Lactancia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Seguro, monitorizar toxicidad GI en infante.","guid":"6qsXHTj6ehrrmJXqoq2OYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"Espectro Antimicrobiano:","guid":"iCu8WT5xtx0SRmG_qUvjNQ","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• Amplio espectro ⬇️ Gram (-), menos efectivo contra bacterias resistentes como P. aeruginosa.","guid":"BedjykI3JamG7UqR87FFcA","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"1. Open Forum Infect Dis. 2024;11(5):ofae214.","guid":"WSpeUAP-iNpsDojdA9c3Rw","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":42,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Urología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Urología","filename":"Ertapenem-2024","id":"map_2380","resolved_references":[]}